{"type":"message","id":"454f3cd4","parentId":"86535dfa","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:44:08.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants Cursor to check if it has a crawler/爬虫 skill. Let me add this as context to the existing skills query task, or create a new task asking specifically about crawler capabilities."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k0kvywlj199g_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\ADHD_agent\\openclaw\\workspace\\cursor_inbox\\task_20260402_004310_crawler.json","content":"{\n  \"title\": \"查询 Cursor Agent 是否有爬虫相关技能\",\n  \"instructions\": \"请确认 Cursor Agent 是否具备以下能力，如果具备请说明具体用法：\\n\\n1. **爬虫/数据抓取能力**：能否抓取网页内容、解析 HTML、从页面提取数据？\\n2. **是否接入了 MediaCrawler**：能否操作小红书、抖音、B站、微博等平台的爬虫？\\n3. **其他数据采集方式**：是否有 API 调用、Selenium/Playwright 等浏览器自动化能力？\\n\\n用户想知道他之前配置的 MediaCrawler MCP 服务（小红书、抖音爬虫）是否能在 Cursor 里直接使用。\\n\\n已知信息：\\n- 本机 MediaCrawler MCP 运行在端口 18080\\n- 小红书 MCP 运行在端口 18060（Docker 容器 xiaohongshu-mcp）\\n\\n请明确回答 Cursor 能否调用这些爬虫能力。\",\n  \"context\": \"用户想知道 Cursor Agent 是否有爬虫/数据抓取相关的技能，特别是他配置的那些 MCP 服务（MediaCrawler、小红书 MCP）能否在 Cursor 里使用。\",\n  \"submitted_by\": \"OpenClaw\",\n  \"priority\": \"normal\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775061836155}}
